{"tid":844714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生太像前夫　失婚高校女教師譜師生戀被捕","createTime":"2018-10-02T05:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T05:51:01.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2269fbccf377b5ca2c341aaf691260f3d6ee04a2","tid":844714,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:39:12.000Z","msg":"俄亥俄州一名失婚女教師，據報因為一名未成年學生，外貌、舉止太像前夫，而與對方成為情侶，更於校內進行性行為而被捕。<br />\n<br />\n被捕女子是32歲的Laura Bucy，她於Twinsburg巿一間高中任教經濟。警方表示，她今年8月曾探訪前夫的父親，並向對方懺悔，透露自己在前一個學期，與一名未成年學生發生性關係。警方上月初訪問Bucy的前夫時，獲得有關消息，之後便拘捕了Bucy，控以性暴行及向未成年人士派發有害物質。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，Bucy向警方作供表示，涉事學生「外貌和舉止太像前夫」，自己才把持不住，並承認兩人曾在教職員的休息室性交，又為對方買電子菸補充劑，容許對方在自己的辦公室吸電子菸。另外，她亦承認曾向另一名學生，購買總值10元（美元、下同）的大麻。<br />\n<br />\n目前，Bucy准以5萬元保釋，被校方停職候查，同時勒令不得再接觸未成年青少年。案件本周四再訊。（北美中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"fc5d80bf56c2ceabfb4525a3d81fb7f09f825a3a","tid":844714,"uid":105888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:39:49.000Z","msg":"等圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5b5a08bc6d14920a097056de94a969232cf66a","tid":844714,"uid":34022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:41:45.000Z","msg":"快點強姦我"},{"pid":"66c78034e1cb1877b4f39c61b4624bc2d98bbb1c","tid":844714,"uid":60052,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:41:53.000Z","msg":"自己睇, 法官大人我就唔屌既。<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.nbc4i.com/news/state-news/teacher-charged-with-having-sex-with-student-in-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbc4i.com%2Fnews%2Fstate-news%2Fteacher-charged-with-having-sex-with-student-in-&d=GBi8YXmaH8y%2Brevsq%2Fz6V%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=326b20b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nbc4i.com/news/state-news/teacher-charged-with-having-sex-with-student-in-</a><br />\nclassroom/1483073802[/url]"},{"pid":"a0d2bb81f314d083684c47e8227545402569a0c8","tid":844714,"uid":34022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66c78034e